      <svg slot="vignette-2" viewBox="0 0 200 220" role="img" aria-labelledby="vm-g-t"><title id="vm-g-t">An unfinished sumi-e ensō with wet-ink trailing to dry-brush and a hidden gold smile at the arrested point</title>
